# Scalar Multiplier

## Overview
Performs multiplication between two scalar values.

## Board
Arty A7 (Artix-7)

## Tools
- Verilog
- Xilinx Vivado

## Description
Takes two input operands and produces their multiplication result.

## Inputs
- Operand A
- Operand B

## Outputs
- Result

## Notes
Demonstrates basic arithmetic design using combinational logic.
